I don't know about Pops.

03:12.000 --> 03:13.790
I mean, what was
his childhood like?

03:13.790 --> 03:15.210
Who are his friends?

03:15.210 --> 03:17.330
Why does he
still own a pager?

03:17.330 --> 03:18.790
That's my question.

03:20.960 --> 03:23.460
