a nickname, too.

08:44.960 --> 08:47.040
"Boy!
Get away from my car."

08:48.500 --> 08:52.290
You can't blame him.
That '73 was special.

08:52.290 --> 08:55.250
You have no idea what
he had to do to get this car.

08:55.250 --> 08:57.620
See, it was the 1970s.

08:57.620 --> 09:00.960
Brothers had come back from
Vietnam broke and strung out.

09:00.960 --> 09:02.960
But Earl was riding
'round these streets

09:02.960 --> 09:05.040
