09:05.040 --> 09:06.540
So, one day, Earl gets fired

09:06.540 --> 09:09.330
for stealing mattresses
from his job.

09:09.330 --> 09:11.380
Thing is, he didn't do it.

09:11.380 --> 09:15.620
So Earl figures, "I'll show
you racists what stealing is,"

09:15.620 --> 09:18.750
and robbed the place blind.

09:18.750 --> 09:21.880
Sold those mattresses on
the street, made his car note.

09:21.880 --> 09:23.750
He may have lost his job,

09:23.750 --> 09:26.330
but he was not
about to lose Black Beauty.

09:26.330 --> 09:27.670
He had that car
all the way up

09:27.670 --> 09:29.880
'til the moment he traded it
for that boat.

09:29.880 --> 09:31.250
I wonder what ever
happened to that.

09:37.500 --> 09:38.670
I don't know.

09:38.670 --> 09:41.120
♪♪

09:41.120 --> 09:43.080
Hey, Mom.
Hmm?

09:43.080 --> 09:44.460
You want to paint
with us?

09:44.460 --> 09:45.830
